      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Infinite limits\n",
        "\n",
        "* Consider the integral $$ \\int_{-\\infty}^\\infty e^{-x^2} \\,dx $$"
      ],
      "id": "b96a9f9b"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "f = lambda x: np.exp(-x**2)\n",
        "\n",
        "val, err = integrate.quad(f, -np.inf, np.inf, epsabs=1.49e-14, epsrel=1.49e-14)"
